description: Crunchfish AB engages in the software development for augmented and virtual reality. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane. The company went IPO on 2016-11-11. The firm operates as a developer of software and services for mobile interaction. The firm mainly specializes in two technologies, such as touchless interaction by gestures and proximity software for mobiles. The firm's Touchless A3D technology detects and tracks objects in three dimensions relying on the video stream from the embedded camera in a mobile device. The firm's aBubbl software development kit is a beacon based intelligent proximity layer that enables a host app to offer user interaction based on real-time presence. The firm operates globally with customers including original equipment manufacturers (OEMs), app developers and service providers world wide.
name: Crunchfish AB
